FT  20 NOV 93 / Shipyard wins Nato contract
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A &amp; P Appledore's shipyard at Falmouth, Cornwall, has won the contract to
refit Nato's research vessel Alliance, which is used to detect and track
submarines.
