</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P5719 Miscellaneous Homefurnishings Stores.
    P5611 Men's and Boys' Clothing Stores.
    P5621 Women's Clothing Stores.
    P5311 Department Stores.
</IN>
