FT  19 NOV 93 / World News in Brief: Cricket libel case settled
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A High Court libel hearing ended after former Pakistan bowler Sarfraz Nawaz
dropped a damages claim against former England batsman Allan Lamb over
allegations concerning Nawaz's bowling technique.
